<taxonomicName id="4C423ED23601D0695488FD5CFCB749F4" authorityName="Westwood" authorityYear="1833" box="[763,908,675,701]" class="Insecta" family="Eulophidae" genus="Aprostocetus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B93699433601D0695488FD5CFCB749F4" box="[763,908,675,701]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">Aprostocetus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the key by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD338A03601D0695256FD5CFBF449F4" author="Graham, M. W. R. de V." box="[1061,1231,675,701]" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="1 - 392" refId="ref18896" refString="Graham, M. W. R. de V. (1987) A reclassification of the European Tetrastichinae (Hymenoptera: Eulophidae), with a revision of certain genera. Bulletin of the British Museum (Natural History), Entomology Series, 55, 1 - 392." type="journal article" year="1987">Graham (1987)</bibRefCitation>
but have affinities to other subgenera; these are discussed under the ‘comments’ section of each species.
